description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an experienced, enthusiastic and self-motivated Administrator to provide full-time support to members of the Central Oxon CAMHS team (Children &amp; Adolescent Mental Health Service), based at Raglan House, Cowley Oxford.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you believe you have a flexible ‘can do’ attitude, with strong administrative, interpersonal, &amp; telephone skills, along with the desire to be part of a friendly, busy admin team who support medics, clinicians and service users, where every day is different, then this could be the job for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
